visual.name: candlestickByOKViz
visual.description: Candlestick by OKViz is used to describe price movements of a security, derivative, or currency. Each candle in the chart typically shows four price values: high, low, open, and close. This visual allows you to define multiple trend lines for analysis purposes, such as the Bollinger Bands.
